--- Jobshaker Installation ---

1. Install Python 2.7 and Django 1.3.1

2. Download and install the following modules

django-registration
https://bitbucket.org/ubernostrum/django-registration/
* you MUST use the source version to avoid simple.urls errors

django-autocomplete
https://bitbucket.org/tyrion/django-autocomplete/

3. Create a new database or connect your own

mkdir db
python manage.py syncdb

4. Load baseline data

Download PLZ light here: https://match.post.ch/ - or:
$ wget https://match.post.ch/download?file=10000&tid=10&rol=0
$ unzip plz_l_20120201.zip db/
$ python load_plz.py

5. Run

python manage.py runserver 0.0.0.0:8000

